    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''The Expanding Meatball Universe'' (June 6):</p>
        <p>Your article failed to mention the meatballs at Carmine's. It was this dish that ruined my two-year stint as a vegetarian. And what a way to go. I think there are at least seven different animals in those things.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''The Expanding Meatball Universe'' (June 6):</p>
        <p>Your article failed to mention the meatballs at Carmine's. It was this dish that ruined my two-year stint as a vegetarian. And what a way to go. I think there are at least seven different animals in those things.</p>
        <p>No other meatballs compare in juiciness and tenderness. Now I say I am a meatball-aterian.</p>
        <p>Susan Behrens  Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
